66916fbe21d16f2064c95d4081d183eec554804d018dd43a0a02ba8e702f86820d4ee4997536c774f4f61e53929f83abcd4642db488bdc632d25eea94c8eac0f  DBD-mysql-4.043-Fix-build-failures-for-MariaDB-10.2.patch"
